{
  "text": "Evaluation of hematological parameters. Hemoglobin (Hb) estimation was done by Sahli's hemometer (Marienfeld Lab. Glassware, Germany) and total leukocyte count (TLC) estimation was done by the method of Khynriam and Prasad [CITATION_1] . Mortality rate. Mortality rate was calculated in order to estimate the overall mortality among different group of animals.",
